If strUnvalidiatedPath points to a valid directory then m_strLastDataListPath the directory If strUnvalidiatedPath points to a valid file then m_strLastDataListPath the file's directory If strUnvalidiatedPath does not point to a valid file or directory then the value 'Nothing' is returned
